    "This allows them to detect the size, shape, distance, and even texture of objects, as well as the speed and direction of their movement.",
    "So, the observer-centric conscious phenomenological experience of the bat can be defined by its sensors, and its cognitive ability to predictively map size, shape, distance, and",
